076 1.34942ZM15.5427 14.8398H7.55223L8.96707 13.425H15.5427V14.8398ZM3.39382 9.78422C2.965 10.213 2.84244 10.3436 2.75709 10.49C2.67183 10.6366 2.61862 10.8079 2.45733 11.3925L2.13099 12.5756C2.00183 13.0439 1.92194 13.3419 1.88863 13.5536C2.10041 13.5204 2.39872 13.4416 2.86764 13.3123L4.05075 12.9859C4.63544 12.8246 4.80669 12.7715 4.95323 12.6862C5.09968 12.6008 5.23022 12.4783 5.65905 12.0494L10.721 6.98644L8.45577 4.72121L3.39382 9.78422ZM11.7 2.57079C11.3774 2.38198 10.9777 2.38198 10.6551 2.57079C10.5602 2.62647 10.4487 2.72931 10.0449 3.13311L9.45604 3.72094L11.7213 5.98617L12.3102 5.39833C12.7139 4.99457 12.8168 4.88307 12.8725 4.78818C13.0613 4.46561 13.0612 4.06585 12.8725 3.74326C12.8169 3.64827 12.7146 3.53752 12.3102 3.13311C11.9057 2.72863 11.795 2.6264 11.7 2.57079Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div><div class="ds-focus-ring"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="_4f9bf79 d7dc56a8 _43c05b5" data-virtual-list-item-key="16" style="--assistant-last-margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="ds-message _63c77b1" style="--panel-width: 0px;"><div class="ds-markdown" style="--ds-md-zoom: 1.143;"><h1><span>📸 Here's How to Upload Your Screenshot to GitHub</span></h1><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Great screenshot! I can see your live site has:</span></p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>50+ Artisans</span></strong><span> (not infinite - update your README!)</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>6 regions</span></strong><span> ✅</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>25+ Products</span></strong><span> ✅</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>100% Authentic</span></strong><span> (even better than 99%!)</span></p></li></ul><hr><h1><span>🖱️ CLICK-BY-CLICK: Upload Your Screenshot</span></h1><h2><span>Step 1: Save the Screenshot to Your Computer</span></h2><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Your screenshot is already in the chat!</span></strong><span> Here's how to save it:</span></p><h3><span>On Desktop:</span></h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Right-click</span></strong><span> on the image in our chat</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Click "Save image as..."</span></strong></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Save as:</span></strong><span> </span><code>gebeya-homepage.png</code></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Save to:</span></strong><span> Your Desktop (easy to find)</span></p></li></ol><h3><span>Alternative - Take a Fresh Screenshot:</span></h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Open</span></strong><span> </span><a href="https://gebeya-b.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>https://gebeya-b.vercel.app</span></a></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Press</span></strong><span> </span><code>Windows + Shift + S</code><span> (Windows) or </span><code>Cmd + Shift + 4</code><span> (Mac)</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Drag</span></strong><span> to capture the whole page</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Save</span></strong><span> as </span><code>gebeya-homepage.png</code></p></li></ol><hr><h2><span>Step 2: Go to Your GitHub Repo</span></h2><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Open</span></strong><span> </span><a href="https://github.com/bamites1-sketch/gebeya-b" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>https://github.com/bamites1-sketch/gebeya-b</span></a></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Look for</span></strong><span> this button near the top:</span></p></li></ol><div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><div class="md-code-block-banner-wrap"><div class="md-code-block-banner md-code-block-banner-lite"><div class="_121d384"><div class="d2a24f03"><span class="d813de27">text</span></div><div class="d2a24f03 _246a029"><div class="efa13877"><button role="button" aria-disabled="false" class="ds-atom-button ds-text-button ds-text-button--with-icon" style="margin-right: 4px;"><div class="ds-icon ds-atom-button__icon" style="font-size: 16px; width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 3px;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.14929 4.02032C7.11197 4.02032 7.87983 4.02016 8.49597 4.07598C9.12128 4.13269 9.65792 4.25188 10.1415 4.53106C10.7202 4.8653 11.2008 5.3459 11.535 5.92462C11.8142 6.40818 11.9334 6.94481 11.9901 7.57012C12.0459 8.18625 12.0458 8.95419 12.0458 9.9168C12.0458 10.8795 12.0459 11.6473 11.9901 12.2635C11.9334 12.8888 11.8142 13.4254 11.535 13.909C11.2008 14.4877 10.7202 14.9683 10.1415 15.3025C9.65792 15.5817 9.12128 15.7009 8.49597 15.7576C7.87984 15.8134 7.11196 15.8133 6.14929 15.8133C5.18667 15.8133 4.41874 15.8134 3.80261 15.7576C3.1773 15.7009 2.64067 15.5817 2.1571 15.3025C1.5784 14.9683 1.09778 14.4877 0.76355 13.909C0.484366 13.4254 0.365184 12.8888 0.308472 12.2635C0.252649 11.6473 0.252808 10.8795 0.252808 9.9168C0.252808 8.95418 0.252664 8.18625 0.308472 7.57012C0.365184 6.94481 0.484366 6.40818 0.76355 5.92462C1.09777 5.34589 1.57839 4.86529 2.1571 4.53106C2.64067 4.25188 3.1773 4.13269 3.80261 4.07598C4.41874 4.02017 5.18666 4.02032 6.14929 4.02032ZM6.14929 5.37774C5.16181 5.37774 4.46634 5.37761 3.92566 5.42657C3.39434 5.47472 3.07859 5.56574 2.83582 5.70587C2.4632 5.92106 2.15354 6.2307 1.93835 6.60333C1.79823 6.8461 1.70721 7.16185 1.65906 7.69317C1.6101 8.23385 1.61023 8.92933 1.61023 9.9168C1.61023 10.9043 1.61009 11.5998 1.65906 12.1404C1.70721 12.6717 1.79823 12.9875 1.93835 13.2303C2.15356 13.6029 2.46321 13.9126 2.83582 14.1277C3.07859 14.2679 3.39434 14.3589 3.92566 14.407C4.46634 14.456 5.16182 14.4559 6.14929 14.4559C7.13682 14.4559 7.83224 14.456 8.37292 14.407C8.90425 14.3589 9.21999 14.2679 9.46277 14.1277C9.83535 13.9126 10.145 13.6029 10.3602 13.2303C10.